# Lag shot speed ladder: power (20 mph / 352.0 ips).
# Cue starts on the second diamond from the bottom, centered left/right,
# and is hit perfectly square toward the top rail.
table brunswick_gc4_9ft
ball cue at (2.0, 2.0)
cue_strike(default).mass_ratio(1.0).energy_loss(0.1)
shot(cue).heading(0deg).speed(power).tip(side: 0.0R, height: 0.0R).using(default)
